{"tid":1112260,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"心穎依然年輕，求大家俾啲空間佢","createTime":"2019-04-17T10:16:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-17T10:46:30.000Z","uid":177082,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1aa2669e9607c1123275aeead4658f0f4b00a8ae","tid":1112260,"uid":177082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T10:16:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">挺身維護黃心穎 馬國明:佢好年輕仲有好多路要行<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n談到女友黃心穎，馬明說:「我唯一可以代她說少少，其實我知道她知自己做錯，她都好想出來跟大家說兩句，但公司擔心她情緒不太穩定，怕會說錯話。<br />\n我知道她剛在IG發文， 她依然很年輕，未來還有好多路要行要走，希望大家給予他空間 。<br />\n至於我，大家不需要替我擔心，我會專心工作，我仍然要拍劇開工，亦不希望影響到拍攝進度。 <br />\n另外安仔自己都說了話，但我是不會發表任何意見，因為這世界上無人有權去發言，除了安仔太太之外，希望盡快可以平息事件。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/life/ent/realtime/1481892/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Flife%2Fent%2Frealtime%2F1481892%2F&d=BZ3h%2BuUaIL2OU9i9OZdAr4VlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=2c337682\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Flife%2Fent%2Frealtime%2F1481892%2F&h=b48c9413\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/life/ent/realtime/1481892/</a>"},{"pid":"a9867ef2f6261be60eaa56801288d305a5ad3b61","tid":1112260,"uid":177082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T10:19:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/04/17/181853_258ef22e3f69403b40389e1798447408.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F04%2F17%2F181853_258ef22e3f69403b40389e1798447408.png&h=4ae6d544&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FbyBpPm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFbyBpPm.png&h=07c5055b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a33cccf5f7d63423f762afc63cc2738d208a1d05","tid":1112260,"uid":177082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T10:19:53.000Z","msg":"馬明<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 